unittitle_ssm: Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Printed Ephemera Collection of Oversized Material
abstract_ssm: The Tamiment Library and Robert F. Wagner Labor Archives Printed Ephemera Collection of Oversized Material is an artificial collection, collected and assembled by the Tamiment Library over the course of several decades. It includes material related to other Printed Ephemera Collections at the Tamiment Library. Most of the material corresponds to organizations in PE 036, trade unions in PE 001, or individuals in PE 030.
